										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It&rsquo;s finally official.  The first draft of Clockwork Twist, book 12, is written.  I just finished it, and now have to edit till it&rsquo;s perfect.  But at the moment it&rsquo;s 70k words long, and wraps up the whole series in a neat little bow.  I&rsquo;ll be releasing Book 6 this year, but starting next year I&rsquo;ll be putting out 2 books a year until the series is done.  Holy hell, I can hardly believe I did all that.  O__O</p>
